# peekdiff environment
#
# Public repos need NOTHING here — the /api/diff proxy works unauthenticated.
# Auth is only required to view PRIVATE repositories.
#
# ⚠️ NEVER put real secrets in this file — it is committed. Copy it to
#    .env.local (gitignored) and fill in real values there.
#
# OAuth App — one "Login with GitHub" grants access to EVERY repo you can access
# (owner or contributor), no per-repo install. Register at:
# Settings -> Developer settings -> OAuth Apps -> New OAuth App.
# Callback URL: <your-origin>/api/github/callback
GITHUB_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
GITHUB_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=
